    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i'll try that. honestly though the shaking is getting kind of bad now and i feel a bit dizzy too. i'm pretty sure it's just because i'm dehydrated or something. like if i just double my water intake and take the magnesium today, i'll be fine by tomorrow right? i really dont want to go to the er or anything if i can help it.",
